<i>they live without being discovered.</i>

133
00:09:09.782 --> 00:09:11.918  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>But the problem is</i>
<i>how to contact them--</i>

134
00:09:11.984 --> 00:09:12.985  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kaito] Kei.

135
00:09:13.853 --> 00:09:14.987  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm back.

136
00:09:17.557 --> 00:09:21.260  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh. Yeah. Welcome back. [gasps]

137
00:09:21.327 --> 00:09:24.564  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kaito] Huh? What is it?

138
00:09:24.630 --> 00:09:27.567  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh? Oh. Nothing.

139
00:09:29.936 --> 00:09:31.704  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Let's rest until nightfall.

140
00:09:32.705 --> 00:09:34.307  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We can switch off every hour.

141
00:09:34.574 --> 00:09:35.575  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay.

142
00:09:35.975 --> 00:09:37.777  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh, yeah.

143
00:09:39.946 --> 00:09:40.947  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Here.

144
00:09:45.851 --> 00:09:47.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kaito yawns]

145
00:09:58.164 --> 00:09:59.165  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kai.

146
00:10:00.099 --> 00:10:01.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Thanks.

147
00:10:05.905 --> 00:10:09.241  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So, uh...
are you really telling me the truth?

148
00:10:09.308 --> 00:10:10.710  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Will you help Kai?

149
00:10:11.711 --> 00:10:14.046  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hmm. You have my word.

150
00:10:16.749 --> 00:10:20.252  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
And you wanna know
what kind of person my brother is?

151
00:10:20.953 --> 00:10:24.023  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yeah, just tell us anything
that comes to mind.

152
00:10:27.159 --> 00:10:30.663  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm not just saying this
because I found out my brother's an Ajin.

153
00:10:31.397 --> 00:10:33.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
If I had to describe him in one word...

154
00:10:35.768 --> 00:10:38.037  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[mother] You can't play
with Kaito anymore.

155
00:10:38.104 --> 00:10:41.374  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kei] Why? You can't just tell me
without a reason.

156
00:10:43.342 --> 00:10:47.980  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Okay, are you listening?
Kaito is the son of a criminal.

157
00:10:50.383 --> 00:10:52.051  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] Oh, well, in that case...

158
00:10:53.819 --> 00:10:57.056  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I was only hanging out with him
'cause he was always alone.

159
00:10:59.392 --> 00:11:02.194  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
My brother... is the worst.

160
00:11:02.261 --> 00:11:05.297  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Sato] Hmm.
That's a pretty bold statement.

161
00:11:06.298 --> 00:11:08.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Is there anything else
you can remember?

162
00:11:10.102 --> 00:11:12.738  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Not really. That's about it.

163
00:11:13.739 --> 00:11:15.841  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Sato] I see. Thanks.

164
00:11:16.442 --> 00:11:19.345  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Well, then, that's all we need from you.

165
00:11:20.112 --> 00:11:21.247  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh?

166
00:11:22.114 --> 00:11:23.115  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What?

167
00:11:24.950 --> 00:11:25.918  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[whimpers]

168
00:11:25.985 --> 00:11:27.887  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What are you...?

169
00:11:38.864 --> 00:11:39.799  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kaito grunts]

170
00:11:59.885 --> 00:12:02.288  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kei] <i>I need the Internet</i>
<i>to find other Ajins.</i>

171
00:12:02.822 --> 00:12:07.193  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>And for that, I need Kai's cell phone</i>
<i>since he hasn't been identified yet.</i>

172
00:12:07.259 --> 00:12:10.396  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>But that's not</i>
<i>the only reason why I need it.</i>

173
00:12:11.730 --> 00:12:13.232  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>There's another possibility.</i>

174
00:12:13.299 --> 00:12:17.269  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Other Ajins might be searching for me.</i>

175
00:12:17.336 --> 00:12:21.073  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>If that's the case, they would do it</i>
<i>through a certain person.</i>

176
00:12:21.140 --> 00:12:23.008  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[cell phone buzzes, then Kei gasps]

177
00:12:23.075 --> 00:12:23.943  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ERIKO

178
00:12:24.009 --> 00:12:25.411  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>Yes.</i>

179
00:12:25.478 --> 00:12:26.779  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Eriko.</i>

180
00:12:27.847 --> 00:12:29.915  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>But the same goes for the police.</i>

181
00:12:29.982 --> 00:12:32.751  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>I don't think Eriko would tell the police</i>
<i>about Kai,</i>

182
00:12:32.818 --> 00:12:35.955  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>but I need to make sure anyway.</i>

183
00:12:36.922 --> 00:12:39.058  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[woman on machine]<i> No one can take</i>
<i>your call right now.</i>

184
00:12:39.125 --> 00:12:41.393  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Please leave a message after the tone.</i>

185
00:12:41.460 --> 00:12:44.330  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>Humans or Ajins...</i>

186
00:12:46.532 --> 00:12:50.002  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Sato over phone] <i>Have you ever seen...</i>
<i>a black ghost?</i>

187
00:12:50.069 --> 00:12:51.003  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

188
00:12:54.306 --> 00:12:55.508  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
This is Nagai.

189
00:12:56.408 --> 00:12:58.077  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[laughing]

190
00:12:58.310 --> 00:13:00.779  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I didn't think you'd answer yourself.

191
00:13:01.547 --> 00:13:03.482  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>You're Ajins, right?</i>

192
00:13:03.549 --> 00:13:05.351  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Indeed we are.

193
00:13:05.951 --> 00:13:07.153  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why do you have my sister's phone?

194
00:13:07.219 --> 00:13:10.990  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>To find out,</i>
<i>come to the place we tell you to.</i>

195
00:13:11.824 --> 00:13:13.292  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Do you have transportation?</i>

196
00:13:14.960 --> 00:13:15.961  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] Yeah.

197
00:13:20.032 --> 00:13:24.270  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kei] <i>There are probably two types</i>
<i>of Ajins living in secret.</i>

198
00:13:24.336 --> 00:13:29.375  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>A quiet type that keeps to himself</i>
<i>and a dangerous type.</i>

199
00:13:30.376 --> 00:13:34.914  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>And if that danger threatens</i>
<i>innocent people...</i>

200
00:13:38.050 --> 00:13:39.418  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[engine revs]

201
00:13:39.485 --> 00:13:41.220  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
If that happens...

202
00:13:43.155 --> 00:13:44.823  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'll kill them.

203
00:13:55.334 --> 00:13:56.468  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[coughs]

204
00:13:58.537 --> 00:14:00.940  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>Damn, I may die of dehydration.</i>

205
00:14:01.574 --> 00:14:06.278  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>But if I die, where does the sodium</i>
<i>and water I lost come back from?</i>

206
00:14:14.386 --> 00:14:17.489  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>If this talk</i>
<i>with the other Ajins goes south,</i>

207
00:14:17.556 --> 00:14:21.493  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>even if I can't be killed,</i>
<i>I could be captured instead.</i>

208
00:14:22.194 --> 00:14:24.063  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
But that doesn't matter now.

209
00:14:24.129 --> 00:14:25.397  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I have no choice...

210
00:14:26.165 --> 00:14:27.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
but to meet them.

211
00:14:37.343 --> 00:14:38.611  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What's with the outfit?

212
00:14:40.112 --> 00:14:43.349  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm sorry,
I didn't have a change of clothes.

213
00:14:43.415 --> 00:14:45.384  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I tried to choose
the plainest clothes in--

214
00:14:45.451 --> 00:14:46.452  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Your report.

215
00:14:47.319 --> 00:14:51.156  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Right. Eriko Nagai was taken
three hours ago.

216
00:14:51.223 --> 00:14:53.259  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
"Tanaka" and "The Hat Guy" were
the ones--

217
00:14:53.325 --> 00:14:54.660  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I don't care about that.

218
00:14:55.527 --> 00:14:59.498  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I want to hear about how the battle
between the black ghosts went.

219
00:15:00.432 --> 00:15:01.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yes, of course.

220
00:15:01.367 --> 00:15:02.234  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[phone rings]

221
00:15:02.301 --> 00:15:03.269  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Well--
-Wait.

222
00:15:04.003 --> 00:15:05.604  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
This is Detective Araki.

223
00:15:06.305 --> 00:15:09.074  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Eriko Nagai's cell phone has been used
just once after her abduction.

224
00:15:09.141 --> 00:15:12.044  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The station figured out
the area it called from.

225
00:15:12.111 --> 00:15:13.445  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Follow the source of that signal.

226
00:15:13.512 --> 00:15:17.983  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Whoever has their hands on that cell phone
seems to be trying to reach Kei Nagai.

227
00:15:19.385 --> 00:15:20.586  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Understood.</i>

228
00:15:35.968 --> 00:15:38.037  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's a nice, quiet place, isn't it?

229
00:15:38.570 --> 00:15:43.208  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
No visitors ever come,
and even the priest almost never shows up.

230
00:15:44.076 --> 00:15:47.146  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>Mr. Sato and--</i>

231
00:15:48.380 --> 00:15:49.281  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

232
00:16:04.129 --> 00:16:05.130  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kaito] Huh?

233
00:16:06.198 --> 00:16:07.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei?

234
00:16:14.406 --> 00:16:16.241  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
He went off by himself.

235
00:16:20.746 --> 00:16:22.381  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei!

236
00:16:22.448 --> 00:16:23.983  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei!

237
00:16:29.421 --> 00:16:31.523  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

238
00:16:43.569 --> 00:16:44.603  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Eriko] Kai...

239
00:16:47.106 --> 00:16:49.742  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I don't think my brother's coming.

240
00:16:51.443 --> 00:16:52.444  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kaito] Yeah.

241
00:16:53.445 --> 00:16:54.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
He called me.

242
00:17:02.254 --> 00:17:03.689  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Summer again, huh?

243
00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:09.762  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[groans]

244
00:17:16.235 --> 00:17:20.105  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Sato] We figured this was the fastest way
to get you to believe us.

245
00:17:20.706 --> 00:17:22.074  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>You're real.</i>

246
00:17:23.442 --> 00:17:24.610  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Should I do it, too?

247
00:17:24.676 --> 00:17:27.579  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Sato] No, you don't need to.
You're already famous.

248
00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:29.515  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So is he.

249
00:17:32.217 --> 00:17:35.621  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kei] <i>Tanaka?!</i>
<i>The second Ajin in the country.</i>

250
00:17:35.687 --> 00:17:39.658  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>There was nothing on the news.</i>
<i>Did he actually break out?</i>

251
00:17:40.759 --> 00:17:42.327  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>He looks dangerous.</i>

252
00:17:46.165 --> 00:17:47.232  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Tanaka scoffs]

253
00:17:48.367 --> 00:17:51.070  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Well, then, let's get straight
to the point.

254
00:17:51.136 --> 00:17:55.107  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Just as I said on the phone,
we're prepared to welcome you.

255
00:17:55.641 --> 00:17:57.576  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What you do now is up to you.

256
00:17:58.410 --> 00:18:01.747  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Before I decide,
I have three questions to ask.

257
00:18:02.414 --> 00:18:04.716  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Sato] Only three?
Ask as many as you like.

258
00:18:07.352 --> 00:18:10.522  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
First question. What'd you do to Eriko?

259
00:18:10.589 --> 00:18:11.757  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Sato] We let her go.

260
00:18:12.491 --> 00:18:13.492  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What?

261
00:18:15.327 --> 00:18:17.162  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps] What?

262
00:18:17.229 --> 00:18:21.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[man] Oh. It's okay, miss.
We're almost at the hospital.

263
00:18:21.300 --> 00:18:24.603  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Sato] <i>By now she should be on her way</i>
<i>back to the hospital, but...</i>

264
00:18:26.772 --> 00:18:28.507  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm terribly sorry.

265
00:18:31.110 --> 00:18:33.378  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
This must sound like an excuse, but...

266
00:18:33.445 --> 00:18:36.281  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
this was the only way
we had to meet with you.

267
00:18:36.348 --> 00:18:39.384  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm sure we really frightened your sister.

268
00:18:40.419 --> 00:18:43.755  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
If she's okay, it's fine.
I was just a little worried.

269
00:18:43.822 --> 00:18:45.791  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Please, stop bowing.

270
00:18:46.725 --> 00:18:48.627  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I am really very sorry.

271
00:18:49.495 --> 00:18:50.829  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Anyway, please continue.

